CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg. 12 reads: "Index Department- Left to right: Philip Gallo, typist; James E. Smith, clerk; Harry Levine, clerk, and Harry A. Conte, special utility clerk"
TitMainTitle: Six clerks, including Philip Gallo, James E. Smith, Harry Levine, and Harry A. Conte, gathered around table covered with documents, in Index Department of Allegheny County Prothonotary office with lockers and high windows
